\* Remove/comment  PROPERTY ATDSpec  in  MCEWD998.cfg  to stop Apalache (0.23.1) from complaining about:
 \*  AsyncTerminationDetection.tla:340:30-340:55: unsupported expression: WF_<<active, pending,...

